00:28:43,040 --> 00:28:43,840
Hurry and eat.

576
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:45,240
No, thanks.

577
00:28:46,080 --> 00:28:47,120
I'm good, thanks.

578
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,800
Qi, send me the first one.

579
