589
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:16,600
Let me take a look.

590
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:17,400
Let me do it.

591
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:17,760
OK.

592
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:31,080
After testing the combinations,

593
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:32,760
