595
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:39,760
OK.

596
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:40,600
Alright.

597
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:48,600
Done.

598
00:29:50,120 --> 00:29:51,040
Done already?

599
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,320
All tested.

600
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,320
Awesome, Jia.

601
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:54,600
Awesome, awesome.

602
00:29:59,040 --> 00:29:59,600
How is it?

603
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:00,340
Completed.

604
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,280
Chao.

605
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,160
Thank you.

606
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:11,120
People in flight control can't give up easily.

607
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:13,040
Yes, Chao is right.

608
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,040
Listening to your words

609
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,680
is like listening to your words.

610
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:18,140
It's better than reading ten years of books.

611
00:30:19,840 --> 00:30:22,280
Today, we veterans personally stepped in

612
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,640
