616
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,000
Yes, yes, yes.

617
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,520
Thank you all, seniors.

618
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:35,320
Thank you, seniors.

619
00:30:35,760 --> 00:30:36,960
At least it's a good result.

620
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,000
We'll be leaving now.

621
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:39,400
