622
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,460
Take care, senior.

623
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,300
Take care, senior.

624
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:43,760
Xiao Chao, come back when you have time

625
00:30:43,760 --> 00:30:45,320
