627
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:47,760
Okay, senior.

628
00:30:48,120 --> 00:30:49,250
No problem, senior.

629
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:50,000
Keep it up.

630
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:50,920
Thank you, seniors. Keep it up.

631
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,400
Keep it up. Thanks for your hard work.

632
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:52,320
Thanks for your hard work.

633
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:53,240
Bye.

634
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,200
Thanks for your hard work.

635
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,840
Bye, bye.

636
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:56,240
Thanks.

637
00:30:56,240 --> 00:30:56,680
Thanks. Bye.

638
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:57,210
Let's go.

639
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,800
There should be one last optimized data left, right?

640
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:02,040
Yes, the last step.

641
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,600
Confirmed. Let's start.

642
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:20,800
Seventeen hours.

643
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:24,400
No, what kind of crappy computer is this?

644
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:25,640
This is way too slow,

645
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:26,900
it will never catch up.

646
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:28,680
The computing load is too heavy.

647
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:29,360
What a pity.

648
00:31:41,760 --> 00:31:44,680
Chao, Jia, Yan.

649
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:47,170
Thank you all for today.

650
00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:49,280
We will handle the rest ourselves.

651
00:31:52,760 --> 00:31:53,640
If there's any news,

652
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:55,700
