653
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:19,040
Qin,

654
00:32:19,560 --> 00:32:21,220
how is the competition going?

655
00:32:21,280 --> 00:32:21,920
I managed to squeeze out

656
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:23,980
