657
00:32:24,520 --> 00:32:26,080
Three, three hours?

658
00:32:26,080 --> 00:32:27,610
Are three hours not enough?

659
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:30,850
Let me tell you, I'm working myself to death here.

660
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:32,160
Enough, enough,

661
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:33,720
it's enough.

662
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,320
It's enough.

663
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:37,840
Alright, that's it.

664
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,040
Mr. Qin.

665
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,720
What's the situation on your end?

666
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,520
The software is finished,

667
00:32:47,520 --> 00:32:49,280
but we don't have enough time for data optimization.

668
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:49,920
Right now,

669
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:51,640
