670
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:52,320
Now?

671
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:54,810
I got you three hours of computer time.

672
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:55,960
Is that enough?

673
00:32:55,960 --> 00:32:56,560
Enough.

674
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:57,680
It's enough.

675
00:32:57,800 --> 00:32:59,840
Let's go.

676
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:01,700
We have a computer.

677
00:33:09,720 --> 00:33:10,600
Hurry.

678
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:11,760
Quick.

679
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:12,720
Stop shaking.

680
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:30,080
Go, Wei!

681
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,930
Shut up, my legs are killing me.

682
00:33:33,360 --> 00:33:34,220
I can't hold on.

683
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:36,640
I can't anymore.

684
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:37,160
I can't.

685
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:41,600
Caibao,

686
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:42,640
hurry.

687
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:44,240
Nan.

688
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:47,970
I'll charge!

689
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:51,160
My useless legs!

690
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,320
It's fine.

691
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:58,600
Hurry! Hurry!

692
00:34:17,639 --> 00:34:18,440
Charge!

693
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:03,080
Mr. Gu, the hard drive.

694
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:04,680
What's the panic?

695
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,640
The more critical the moment is,

696
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:08,900
