697
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:15,050
How is it?

698
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:50,960
No way.

699
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:53,200
The World Aerospace Association uploaded a new plan.

700
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:55,160
It's ahead of the second place by over 2,000 points.

701
00:35:55,160 --> 00:35:56,360
Over 2,000 points?

702
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:57,280
What the heck?

703
00:35:59,160 --> 00:35:59,920
Oh my god.

704
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:03,200
What do we do now?

705
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,920
The entire calculation process

706
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:10,040
