707
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:12,080
Worrying won't help.

708
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:13,800
How about this?

709
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:14,840
We take turns.

710
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:18,000
You guys go rest first. I'll keep an eye on things here.

711
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:18,800
Okay.

712
00:36:20,200 --> 00:36:20,720
Mr. Gu.

713
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:22,880
All right.

714
00:36:23,520 --> 00:36:24,980
I'll leave it to you, Ziqi.

715
00:36:25,120 --> 00:36:25,720
Go ahead.

716
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:27,180
Thanks for your hard work.

717
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,820
Let's go. We'll head back.

718
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,860
I'm exhausted.

719
00:36:30,080 --> 00:36:31,610
This BMW is too hard to ride.

720
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:45,440
Mr. Gu, Mr. Gu.

721
00:36:45,720 --> 00:36:48,320
Thank you so much for today.

722
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:49,760
It's nothing.

723
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:54,760
Lao Qin really knows his stuff.

724
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:55,960
Thank you so much too.

725
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:58,240
Show some respect and get your arm off me.

726
00:36:58,240 --> 00:36:59,120
Mind my image.

727
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:00,760
What image?

728
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:02,100
Let me tell you.

729
00:37:02,680 --> 00:37:04,480
About all of Mr. Qin's little secrets,

730
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:05,740
I know them inside out.

731
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:06,760
Tell me more.

732
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:07,360
Really.

733
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,080
Very funny.

734
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:10,440
He's shy.

735
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:11,880
If you want to maintain your image,

736
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:13,160
