737
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:14,120
No, no money.

738
00:37:14,160 --> 00:37:15,680
I have no money, but you can take my life.

739
00:37:15,680 --> 00:37:16,720
Come on.

740
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:24,480
Get up.

741
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:25,560
We won.

742
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:26,480
We won.

743
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:28,240
Say it again.

744
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:32,320
We are the champions. We are number one.

745
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:33,800
What are you eating?

746
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:35,040
Let's go to a restaurant.

747
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:36,120
It's my treat.

748
00:37:36,240 --> 00:37:36,800
Do you know

749
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:38,320
how many points we beat the foreign team by?

750
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:39,760
Over 1,000 points.

751
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:41,200
We finally won the championship.

752
00:37:41,200 --> 00:37:43,400
It's both interesting and meaningful.

753
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,000
We won.

754
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,420
Congratulations.

755
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:55,380
Here, have some steamed buns.

756
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,600
Every time we successfully complete a mission,

757
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:58,730
we eat steamed buns.

758
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,200
Now you know.

759
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:02,420
This is our aerospace tradition.

760
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:05,100
Without your seniors, you wouldn't be here.

761
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,080
Yes, yes, yes.

762
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,920
We sincerely thank our seniors.

763
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:09,840
All right, eat up,

764
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:13,000
little champions.

765
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,160
Congratulations.

766
00:38:14,160 --> 00:38:15,560
Thank you, Director Cao.

767
00:38:15,640 --> 00:38:17,280
I came here specifically to tell you guys.

768
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,880
Hurry up and get ready.

769
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:20,740
There's an award ceremony later.

770
00:38:21,560 --> 00:38:23,760
We have to go abroad to receive the award.

771
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:25,240
Do I have a suit? Do you have one?

772
00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:26,360
Why do you care if I have a suit or not?

773
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:26,920
I have one, I have one.

774
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:27,800
I, I have one.

775
00:38:28,560 --> 00:38:29,800
Going abroad?

776
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:31,400
You're overthinking it.

777
00:38:31,560 --> 00:38:32,440
Receive the award online.

778
00:38:32,440 --> 00:38:33,840
Remember to take a video for me later.

779
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,680
Don't forget.

780
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,600
Receive the award online.

781
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:43,480
Let's eat.

782
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:44,280
Aren't there steamed buns?

783
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:45,720
No more herbal jelly. Eat the buns.

784
00:38:45,720 --> 00:38:47,080
Eat the buns.

785
00:38:47,080 --> 00:38:47,880
Come on.

786
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:52,200
One bite for you, one bite for me.

787
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:53,600
They won.

788
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:56,260
It's not like you got first place.

789
00:38:59,640 --> 00:39:03,120
The topic of this competition is 'Immigrating to the Milky Way'.

790
00:39:03,120 --> 00:39:04,480
In the vast universe,

791
00:39:04,640 --> 00:39:06,700
as intelligent life on a tiny planet,

792
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:09,960
Human exploration of space has never stopped.

793
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:11,080
We believe

794
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:13,440
that at distances measured in light-years,

795
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:15,920
we can see a brighter future.

796
00:39:16,520 --> 00:39:18,320
Earth is the cradle of humanity,

797
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,280
but humanity

798
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:21,210
cannot live in the cradle forever.

799
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:24,800
This interesting and challenging topic

800
00:39:25,080 --> 00:39:25,840
allowed us to try to

801
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:28,040
advance theories and methods,

802
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:30,280
and enjoy the process of the competition.

803
00:39:30,280 --> 00:39:33,320
It not only expanded the dimensions of technology and knowledge,

804
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,240
but also made us firmly believe

805
00:39:34,240 --> 00:39:36,200
that the cause we are engaged in

806
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:39,410
is laying the foundation for the future of all humanity.

807
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,760
Thanks to the organizing committee,

808
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:42,620
and thanks to those who helped us.

809
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:44,160
To win this championship

810
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:45,520
is a great honor for us.

811
00:39:48,080 --> 00:39:50,140
But the people I want to thank the most

812
00:39:51,200 --> 00:39:52,320
are my teammates.

813
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:56,000
Being able to complete this competition

814
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,880
is precisely because we worked together,

815
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,010
fought side by side,

816
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:01,130
to overcome the difficulties.

817
00:40:02,040 --> 00:40:03,300
The beauty of humanity

818
00:40:03,560 --> 00:40:05,160
is not only in distant space,

819
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:06,920
but also right beside us.

820
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:08,680
In Guolai.

821
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:12,120
No matter where humanity eventually goes,

822
00:40:12,560 --> 00:40:13,960
the most important thing

823
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:16,400
will always be the people around us.

824
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:28,600
Take a picture.

825
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:39,600
One, two, three.

826
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:49,440
Qi, are you okay?

827
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:53,120
Don't help me up.

828
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:55,360
No one help me.

829
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:56,400
Don't touch me.

830
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:58,490
Walk in a straight line.

831
00:41:00,680 --> 00:41:02,720
Hold him. What if he really falls?

832
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:04,320
He said no one should help him.

833
00:41:04,320 --> 00:41:04,840
Right?

834
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:12,560
Nan.

835
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,160
You are really outstanding.

836
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:17,720
Awesome.

837
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,760
Be confident.

838
00:41:20,520 --> 00:41:22,050
I know it's not easy for you.

839
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:23,080
You know?

840
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:24,280
Ying Ziqi,

841
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:26,680
watch your behavior in broad daylight.

842
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:28,040
Keep it up.

843
00:41:32,560 --> 00:41:33,440
And you guys,

844
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:35,240
listen to me.

845
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,320
We are Team Muxing.

846
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:43,000
Invincible.

847
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:45,820
The future of the flight control center,

848
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:48,320
