849
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:49,520
Okay.

850
00:41:53,120 --> 00:41:53,800
Ying Ziqi,

851
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:54,600
turn around.

852
00:42:11,200 --> 00:42:12,600
What are you laughing at?

853
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:15,640
It's championship night, can't I be happy?

854
00:42:17,120 --> 00:42:18,520
The competition is over.

855
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:21,700
What's the plan for Team Muxing next?

856
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:25,200
What are your plans?

857
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:27,880
You and Nan...

858
00:42:34,720 --> 00:42:35,760
I won't tease you anymore.

859
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:36,520
Seriously,

860
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:38,120
I'm not bragging,

861
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:39,400
I really think

862
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:41,400
our little team has a bright future.

863
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:44,440
Becoming full-time employees goes without saying.

864
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:46,700
